cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.MM, cs.IT, cs.LG

The paper deals with image fusion and registration, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and graphics (cs.GR). The use of convex optimization and sparsity regularization also suggests a potential fit for machine learning (cs.MM) and information theory (cs.IT). Finally, the computational efficiency aspect of the proposed algorithm may also relate to the field of machine learning (cs.LG).
